OL,4,G0010F999: On the Front Line
OL,5,     GParamedics treat a young man
OL,6,     Gwho's collapsed outside a
OL,7,     Gnightclub and isn't breathing, a
OL,8,     Gyoung woman who's having a sickle
OL,9,     Gcell crisis and a woman with
OL,10,     Gcrippling chest pains.
OL,11,G0115F24 Hours in A&E
OL,12,     GKing's College Hospital in London
OL,13,     Ghas one of Britain's busiest A&E
OL,14,     Gdepartments. In this episode, two
OL,15,     Gcyclists arrive in A&E, and a
OL,16,     Gretired docker takes a shine to
OL,17,     Gnurse Laura.
